outputs.output_descr: As the last in a series of three courthouses, UNDP/PAPP will construct and equip the magistrate and first instance courthouse of Jenin to allow for access to justice, and the efficent processing of cases in Jenin.

project_descr: PAL/ Construction & Equipping of the Magistrate Court & First Instance Court in the City of Jenin
project_title: PAL/Construction & Equipping of the First Instance Court
